ay-lg-c3-oled-sale-deal&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/8/24152110/ebay-lg-c3-oled-sale-deal" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/8/24152110/ebay-lg-c3-oled-sale-deal</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-08T15:22:41-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-08T15:22:41-04:00</updated><title> Epic 诉苹果案中的法官认为苹果在按钮和链接方面存在不正当行为</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;App Store 徽标位于木槌背景前的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7ipFAqEaP3TCG8foMYgvDHdeDzQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73335398/STK468_APPLE_ANTITRUST_CVIRGINIA_C.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;i18tra&quot;>;Epic Games 和 Apple 将在未来几周内于法庭举行证据听证会&lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/1/31/24056751/epic-notice-apple-app-store-outside- payments-link-27-percent&quot;>;苹果是否违反了&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2021/9/12/22667694/epic-v-apple-trial-fortnite-judge-yvonne-gonzalez-rogers-final-ruling-injunction-breakdown&quot;>;反转向禁令&lt; /a>; 由法官 Yvonne Gonzalez Rogers 于 2021 年在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/4/29/22410877/epic-games-apple-app-store-antitrust-Trial 后制定-lawsuit-news&quot;>;具有里程碑意义的审判&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;MZEWeW&quot;>;这些听证会将涉及有关 App Store 指南的大量细节。例如，今天涉及很多关于按钮的问题。 （Apple 限制&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/9/10/22667161/app-store-epic-ruling-difference-button-external-link&quot;>;按钮样式&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24049014/apple-epic-court-ruling-developer-tax&quot;>;超出应用内支付系统&lt;/a>;的链接。）&lt;/p >; &lt;p id=&quot;Rshga4&quot;>;但是罗杰斯法官的这句话对苹果来说看起来不太好：&lt;/p>; &lt;blockquote>;&lt;p id=&quot;CKWc4N&quot;>;我无法想象苹果为什么这样做的逻辑原因会要求竞争对手的应用程序。什么是合乎逻辑的竞争理由，不是建议，而是要求？ ...除了扼杀竞争，我看不出...&lt;/p>;&lt;/blockquote>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/8/24152194/epic -apple-anti-steering-injunction-button-style&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/8/24152194/epic-apple-anti-steering-injunction-button-style" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/8/24152194/epic-apple-anti-steering-injunction-button-style</id><author><name>莎拉·郑</name></author></entry></feed>